5 6. Cash. Cash; and
6 7. Other method approved by director. Any other method approved by the director.
7 An operator may not accept payment for a wager by use of a credit card.
8 SUMMARY
99 This bill specifies the methods of payment that may be used to make a sports wager
1100 and prohibits the use of a credit card to pay for a sports wager.
